""" Images - mix good and bad """
images = Images(['files/0_100.jpg', 'files/nofile.jpg', 'files/1_100.jpg'],
    [0, 1, 2], name='foobar')
self.assertEquals(len(images), 2)
self.assertEquals(images.fail, 1)
images = Images()
images.load('foobar')
self.assertEquals(len(images), 2)
os.remove('foobar.h5')
